---
title: Sesame-Crusted Pork with Carrot Ribbons, Bok Choy and Peanut Noodles
description: Crusting your pork with sesame seeds is an interesting way to add flavour and texture. Served on a bed of delicious peanut noodles, we think you'll be licking this plate clean!
